{"tid":841047,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"毆劫的士司機　年輕情侶落網","createTime":"2018-09-29T09:36:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-03T15:54:28.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"43fc2e9f0f7f1830bc122cc1e533e935494d9028","tid":841047,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T09:36:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180929/20510827\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180929%2F20510827&d=Rk%2FbIM7tdILA6ESJHrBbmP6YfqAiA4jm3R2Vm1010vU%3D&h=f6bc5595\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180929%2F20510827&h=cfe89b37\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180929/20510827</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年09月29日 <br />\n<br />\n毆劫的士司機　年輕情侶落網<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180929/large/29la8p11.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180929%2Flarge%2F29la8p11.jpg&h=9a049987&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n葵涌本月23日發生的士劫案，警員在場調查。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】一對16歲及18歲的年輕賊鴛鴦，4天內打劫及襲擊兩名的士司機，掠去近5,000元財物。警方追查下，前日於粉嶺華明邨拘捕該對情侶。其中一名受傷的士司機事後需縫3針，現時仍未復工，對於年輕賊鴛鴦犯案大感驚訝。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n62歲司機中刀縫3針<br />\n<br />\n被捕16歲少年失學及失業，18歲女友則就讀大專，警方於女方位於華明邨單位內起回一隻手錶，相信是案中失物，又於被捕人士身上撿獲口罩、環保袋及相信案發時身穿的衣物，兩人其後被押返警署扣查。<br />\n<br />\n該對情侶涉嫌於本月20及23日，於打鼓嶺坪輋及葵涌打劫兩名分別46及62歲的士司機，共搶去近5,000元財物，兩名司機皆遇襲受傷。<br />\n<br />\n其中在葵涌遇劫的62歲姓陸的士司機頭、肩受傷，事後送院縫了3針，昨日仍在家休養。他從記者口中得悉賊人落網，坦言「咁後生就打劫，有冇搞錯呀！」並表示日後駕車會提高警覺。<br />\n<br />\n■記者詹家志、周鴻熙  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n兩女網售月餅券騙財被捕<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n港故事： 一刀過刻個半圓　 香港第一鳥蟲文篆刻家"},{"pid":"db2b9d46e09909c5bd0985350e8681d6c9166f94","tid":841047,"uid":149566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T10:03:27.000Z","msg":"真廢青<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e2ca72ba23a531d61a1d7e93eb653a68ac62b5c","tid":841047,"uid":37661,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T10:08:48.000Z","msg":"18歲女友。<br />\n做 ptgf 都夠養埋條仔啦"},{"pid":"2cf8f84b83888de000c0352c71aca192ce0873b9","tid":841047,"uid":22553,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"6e2ca72ba23a531d61a1d7e93eb653a68ac62b5c","tid":841047,"uid":37661,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T10:08:48.000Z","msg":"18歲女友。<br />\n做 ptgf 都夠養埋條仔啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T02:41:59.000Z","msg":"係正既使鳩做賊咩，可能成個欣宜咁款，佢比返錢你都食唔落"},{"pid":"a956ecfae3bfa53a1fd58e2fe831c6b54c2a7808","tid":841047,"uid":204571,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T15:54:28.000Z","msg":"明明讀垃圾青年學院 扮咩讀大專<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}